# Structural template for project .env files. This dotfiles repo does not
# consume any env vars from .env directly. Copy/adapt this format into the
# .env of downstream projects (dbt, airflow, etc.) that expect it.
#
# Machine-local secrets used by Claude or shell tools belong in shell
# config (~/.bashrc, ~/.zshrc) or in ~/.claude/settings.local.json,
# not here.

# GITHUB_PAT=
